l?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FAxmUQ3&h=51b439fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">CityU 香港城市大學 (City University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/TbByx8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTbByx8&h=08d3556c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 2015 年：起用新校徽 logo<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/APKnhz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FAPKnhz&h=f3da7696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1956 年：<ins>香港浸會書院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/gbktgn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fgbktgn&h=f50296c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1972 年：改稱<ins>香港浸會學院 Hong Kong Baptist College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ACbAJ4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FACbAJ4&h=6dfbd898&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/F9QYvP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FF9QYvP&h=929132e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKBU 香港浸會大學 (Hong Kong Baptist University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/aFkVTK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FaFkVTK&h=c02dba86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1991 年</span></span>：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKUST 香港科技大學 (The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology)</span></span> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/LEAwFT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum